## ததஅக

[ vitarppam ]  
  
பெ. vidarbha. thecountry of vidarbha  
modern berar  
one of 56tēcam  
q.v.; தேசம் ஐம்பத்தாறனுள் ஒன்றானதும்தற்காலத்தில் பீரார் என்று வழங்குவதுமான நாடு  
s. a district and city to the s. w. of bengal said to be the country of bheema  
the father of damayanti  
s. a district and city to the southwest of bengal  
the modern baranagpûr  
said to be the country of bhîma the father of தமயந்தி wife of nala raja  
ஓர்தேசம். w. p.   
467. vidarbha. note. the name is said to be given to this country because it produces no தர்ப்பை grass  
in consequence of the curse of a rishi whose son had died of a wound from a blade of the grass  
ஓர் தேயம்